Brown MS, Goldstein JL (Jan 1976). "Receptor-mediated control of cholesterol metabolism". Science. 191 (4223): 150–4. PMID 174194. doi:10.1126/science.174194. 
Goldstein JL, Sobhani MK, Faust JR, Brown MS (Oct 1976). "Heterozygous familial hypercholesterolemia: failure of normal allele to compensate for mutant allele at a regulated genetic locus". Cell. 9 (2): 195–203. PMID 184960. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(76)90110-0. 
Brown MS, Goldstein JL (Dec 1976). "Analysis of a mutant strain of human fibroblasts with a defect in the internalization of receptor-bound low density lipoprotein". Cell. 9 (4 PT 2): 663–74. PMID 189940. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(76)90130-6. 
Anderson RG, Brown MS, Goldstein JL (Mar 1977). "Role of the coated endocytic vesicle in the uptake of receptor-bound low density lipoprotein in human fibroblasts". Cell. 10 (3): 351–64. PMID 191195. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(77)90022-8. 
Goldstein JL, Brown MS, Stone NJ (Nov 1977). "Genetics of the LDL receptor: evidence that the mutations affecting binding and internalization are allelic". Cell. 12 (3): 629–41. PMID 200368. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(77)90263-X. 
Anderson RG, Goldstein JL, Brown MS (1977). "A mutation that impairs the ability of lipoprotein receptors to localise in coated pits on the cell surface of human fibroblasts". Nature. 270 (5639): 695–9. PMID 201867. doi:10.1038/270695a0. 
Anderson RG, Vasile E, Mello RJ, Brown MS, Goldstein JL (Nov 1978). "Immunocytochemical visualization of coated pits and vesicles in human fibroblasts: relation to low density lipoprotein receptor distribution". Cell. 15 (3): 919–33. PMID 215316. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(78)90276-3. 
Goldstein JL, Anderson RG, Brown MS (Jun 1979). "Coated pits, coated vesicles, and receptor-mediated endocytosis". Nature. 279 (5715): 679–85. PMID 221835. doi:10.1038/279679a0. 
Mello RJ, Brown MS, Goldstein JL, Anderson RG (Jul 1980). "LDL receptors in coated vesicles isolated from bovine adrenal cortex: binding sites unmasked by detergent treatment". Cell. 20 (3): 829–37. PMID 6251975. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(80)90329-3. 
Brown MS, Kovanen PT, Goldstein JL (May 1981). "Regulation of plasma cholesterol by lipoprotein receptors". Science. 212 (4495): 628–35. PMID 6261329. doi:10.1126/science.6261329. 
Basu SK, Goldstein JL, Anderson RG, Brown MS (May 1981). "Monensin interrupts the recycling of low density lipoprotein receptors in human fibroblasts". Cell. 24 (2): 493–502. PMID 6263497. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(81)90340-8. 
Tolleshaug H, Goldstein JL, Schneider WJ, Brown MS (Oct 1982). "Posttranslational processing of the LDL receptor and its genetic disruption in familial hypercholesterolemia". Cell. 30 (3): 715–24. PMID 6291781. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(82)90276-8. 
Basu SK, Goldstein JL, Brown MS (Feb 1983). "Independent pathways for secretion of cholesterol and apolipoprotein E by macrophages". Science. 219 (4586): 871–3. PMID 6823554. doi:10.1126/science.6823554. 
Brown MS, Anderson RG, Goldstein JL (Mar 1983). "Recycling receptors: the round-trip itinerary of migrant membrane proteins". Cell. 32 (3): 663–7. PMID 6299572. doi:10.1016/0092-8674(83)90052-1. 
